### Environment
@host = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Root / metadata snapshot
GET {{host}}/api/
Accept: application/json

### Liveness (does not depend on Kafka)
GET {{host}}/api/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Readiness (depends on Kafka)
GET {{host}}/api/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### Actuator health (aggregate)
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Actuator liveness
GET {{host}}/actuator/health/liveness
Accept: application/json

### Actuator readiness
GET {{host}}/actuator/health/readiness
Accept: application/json

### Create order
POST {{host}}/api/create-order
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "orderId": "order-123",
  "numItems": 2
}

### Update order
PUT {{host}}/api/update-order
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "orderId": "order-123",
  "status": "SHIPPED"
}
